{"title_page": "Rejnaldo Troplini", "text_new": "{{short description|Albanian footballer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=January 2015}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Rejnaldo Troplini\n| image = \n| fullname = Rejnaldo Troplini\n| birth_date = {{birth date and age|df=yes|1994|11|9}}\n| birth_place = [[Durr\u00ebs]], [[Albania]]\n| height= {{height|m=1.66}}\n| position = [[Right midfielder]]/[[defender (association football)|defender]]\n| currentclub = [[KF Erzeni]]\n| clubnumber = 9\n| youthyears1 =  {{0}}{{0}}{{0}}{{0}}\u20132013\n| youthclubs1 = [[KF Teuta Durr\u00ebs|Teuta]]\n| years1 =  2013\n| clubs1 =  [[KF Teuta Durr\u00ebs|Teuta]]<ref>[http://kfteuta.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=1287:emer-mbiemer&catid=107:lojtaret&Itemid=635 KF Teuta profile]</ref>\n| caps1 =  0\n| goals1 =  0\n| years2 =  2014\n| clubs2 =  [[KF La\u00e7i|La\u00e7i]]\n| caps2 = 2\n| goals2 = 0\n| years3 = 2014\u2013\n| clubs3 = [[KF Erzeni|Erzeni]]\n| caps3 = 103\n| goals3 = 10\n| nationalyears1 = \n| nationalteam1 =  \n| nationalcaps1 =    \n| nationalgoals1 =   \n| pcupdate = \n| ntupdate = \n}}\n'''Rejnaldo Troplini''' (born 9 November 1994 in [[Durr\u00ebs]]) is an [[Albania]]n football player who currently plays for [[KF Erzeni|Erzeni Shijak]] in the [[Albanian Second Division]].<ref>[https://int.soccerway.com/players/rejnaldo-troplini/269445/ Soccerway profile]</ref><ref>[http://www.fshf.org/garat/components/lojtar.php?player_id=222535 FSHF profile]</ref> His main position is on the right side of the midfield, but he is also capable of playing as a right back.<ref>[http://www.panorama-sport.com/kategoria-superiore/kule-dhe-troplini-dy-te-rinj-ne-radhet-e-kurbinasve/ Kule dhe Troplini, dy t\u00eb rinj n\u00eb radh\u00ebt e kurbinasve]</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Troplini, Rejnaldo}}\n[[Category:1994 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Footballers from Durr\u00ebs]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:As